snippet.title: Ancient Mind Teaser
snippet.description:
Ancient Mind is a game for PC and Mobile currently in development by HexagonNico.

Find your way through dangerous dungeons and uncover their secret.

Ancient Mind is set to be released in 2024.

Support the development: https://ko-fi.com/hexagonnico

** Follow Ancient Mind **
Twitter - https://twitter.com/AncientMindGame
Official Website (WIP) - https://ancient-mind.github.io

** Follow HexagonNico **
Twitter - https://twitter.com/HexagonNico
Itch.io - https://hexagonnico.itch.io

** Credits **
Music - The Black Temple by HitCtrl - https://opengameart.org/content/rpg-exploration-the-black-temple
